## Title
Fedora

## URL
http://fedoraproject.org

## Description
Fresh packages, great new features. Comes with the Gnome 3 desktop environment which is modern and simple to use. Visit http://rpmfusion.org/Configuration after installation and follow the steps.

## Pros
 - Looks very nice by default
 - Simple, but intuitive UI
 - Bleeding edge software
 - Great community
 - Frequent update cycle
 
## Cons
 - Less stable than Debian stable-based distributions
 - Gnome isn't very lightweight
 - Might not be as supported as Debian-based distributions

